data.description: PLEASE NOTE: $20,000 is only the auction starting price. It does not have any bearing on the market value.  Nestled on a sunny corner lot in Jerome, this spacious 1999 manufactured home offers a blank canvas for your renovation dreams. Imagine transforming the 1809 sq ft, 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom layout into your own oasis! The open living area invites cozy gatherings, while the well-equipped kitchen is primed for culinary adventures. Step outside to your private, fully fenced backyard, perfect for barbecues and family playtime. A detached 2-car garage provides ample storage or workshop space, adding to the home's versatility. This property beckons DIY enthusiasts and savvy investors seeking a prime opportunity to personalize and maximize its value. Don't miss your chance to own this spacious home at an exciting auction price on January 17th, 2024! Contact us today and unleash your vision!
